                        "name": "bkarwin",
                        "displayName": "Bill Karwin",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I cannot reproduce any issue here.  We have tests for {{Zend_Db_Table::fetchAll()}} and {{Zend_Db_Table::fetchRow()}} that specify both {{ASC}} and {{DESC}} order and they run fine on all supported databases, including Mysqli.\n\nIf you want to reopen this issue, please provide code for test case that demonstrates a failure.",
